    ElasticSearchControllerTest Tests ElasticSearchController functions by manually setting and checking data with the Jest Client. tests are a bit wordy, most of this stuff will be wrapped up cleanly in usermanager In order for tests to run, Elasticsearch index must be at cmput301f18t01test
